---
title: Creamy Gnocchi with Mushroom and Broccoli
description: Pan-frying gnocchi brings a whole extra dimension to these pillowy little dumplings. The golden, crispy exterior provides a beautiful contrast with today's creamy mushroom sauce. As an added bonus it's incredibly easy to make, leaving you plenty of time to put your feet up. Enjoy!
